    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Ilari Pihlajisto</b>\n</p><p><b>Ilari Pihlajisto</b>,<br />\na Finnish freetime and computer chess programmer. He is author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compatible <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source</a> chess program <a href=\"/Sloppy\" title=\"Sloppy\">Sloppy</a>. Along with <a href=\"/index.php?title=Arto_Jonsson&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Arto Jonsson (page does not exist)\">Arto Jonsson</a>, Ilari is co-author of <a href=\"/Cute_Chess\" title=\"Cute Chess\">Cute Chess</a>, a cross-platform <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">graphical user interface</a> for chess engines that use the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> or <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">Universal Chess Interface</a>, and the <a href=\"/CLI\" title=\"CLI\">command line tool</a> for <a href=\"/Engine_Testing#Matches\" title=\"Engine Testing\">engine-engine matches</a>, <a href=\"/Cutechess-cli\" title=\"Cutechess-cli\">Cutechess-cli</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ilari_Pihlajisto&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27024\">Cutechess-cli: A command line tool for engine-engine matches</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 16, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=293506&amp;t=27024\">Cutechess-cli version 0.1.8 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 29, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41565\">Cutechess-cli 0.5.0 for Linux available</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=44843\">Help us make Cute Chess GUI better</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 20, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48626\">cutechess-cli 0.6.0 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 12, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=57406&amp;start=14\">cutechess-cli 0.7.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 29, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61308\">Cute Chess 0.9.0 (GUI) released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Cute_Chess\" title=\"Cute Chess\">Cute Chess</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ilari_Pihlajisto&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/ilaripih\">ilaripih (Ilari Pihlajisto) · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/cutechess\">Cute Chess · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ilari_Pihlajisto&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27024\">Cutechess-cli: A command line tool for engine-engine matches</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ilari Pihlajisto</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 16, 2009</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301011236\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.006 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 29/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 66/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5919-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301011236 and revision id 26484\n -->\n"
